    "@value" : "Defines the average parameter of a probability distribution, which is the mean of the distribution. This is useful for probability distributions which are defined by their mean and another parameter, such as the normal distribution (defined by its mean and standard deviation) or the Poisson distribution (defined by its mean, which is also its lambda parameter)."
  } ],
