    "@value" : "Defines the utility associated with a health condition, intervention, pathway, population or resource usage item. The utility is a measure of the preference or value that individuals or society assign to a particular health state or outcome. It is often used in health economics and decision analysis to evaluate the desirability of different health outcomes and to inform healthcare decision-making."
